### Packages and Patches
- user root
```
crow@debian:~$ su root
Password: 
```
- To create this directory
```
root@debian:/home/crow# mkdir -v $LFS/sources
mkdir: created directory '/mnt/lfs/sources'
```
- Make this directory writable and sticky
```
root@debian:/home/crow# chmod -v a+wt $LFS/sources
mode of '/mnt/lfs/sources' changed from 0755 (rwxr-xr-x) to 1777 (rwxrwxrwt)
```